      "beast_baseline": "but \"finding peace\" sounds like such a struggle. like wrestling with life just to stay afloat when there’s no point. why would i keep fighting for a peace that only comes when you stop? the \"quiet\" i’m talking about isn't just a mood, it’s the idea that everything is easier once you aren't a part of the equation anymore. it’s easier for everyone, really. it's cleaner.",
